---
// Footer component with open source info, credits, and copyright
---

<footer class="border-t border-[--color-border-light] py-12 md:py-16 px-4 sm:px-6">
  <div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto text-center">
    <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-[--color-text-primary] mb-2">Ralph Vibe</p>
    <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-[--color-text-muted] mb-6">Autonomous development, simplified.</p>

    <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-[--color-text-secondary] mb-6">
      Open source and free to use. Contributions welcome.
    </p>

    <a href="https://github.com/whatiskadudoing/ralph-vibe" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-block px-5 py-2.5 font-medium rounded-lg hover:no-underline transition-colors mb-8" style="background-color: #1A1A1A; color: white;">
      View on GitHub
    </a>

    <div class="border-t border-[--color-border-light] pt-6 mt-2">
      <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-[--color-text-muted] mb-3">
        Inspired by the <a href="https://ghuntley.com/ralph/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-[#C46849] hover:underline">Ralph Wiggum Technique</a> by <a href="https://github.com/ghuntley" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-[#C46849] hover:underline">Geoffrey Huntley</a>
      </p>
      <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-[--color-text-muted]">&copy; 2026 Ralph Vibe. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
